body:
I love participating in other 'Forum Games' so I thought I would make my own.
Hopefully it works well :D

What you have to do is make a nickname of the person above you. Please nothing inappropriate!

For Example:

Tynvale

YOU WOULD SAY SOMETHING LIKE: Tyn

And so on . . .
